 Justification:
 FY 2027 funds will be used to maintain Aircraft operational availability and pilot safety. CAD/PAD assets expire due to established item shelf/service life, or mandatory "time-change" procedures for installed
 devices. In accordance with Technical Order (T.O.) 00-20-1, the aircraft becomes grounded until reliable assets are obtained and installed.

 Funding requested in FY27 adjusted to account for prior years execution issues. The cause of poor execution was due to production issues caused by a very small industrial base. This impacted producing
 these components for the Air Force and affected some year's execution. This reduction is an attempt to properly fund CAD/PAD.




