 Remarks:
 FY 2027 funding request supports organic depot activation efforts at Robins AFB for the High Frequency Radio Systems (HFRS) program for the AN/ARC-260 high Frequency (HF) airborne radio. The AN/ARC-260 program is in the final
 stages of development of the airborne radio for 15 different aircraft platforms and began depot activation efforts in FY 2026.

 FY 2027 depot activation efforts for the HFRS program include procurement of 1 hardware/software test station, 70% completion of the creation of technical data, procurement of tooling and software licenses, interim contractor support (ICS)
 for AN/ARC-260 repairs, modifications to the existing repair line and program support costs.

 Funding for this exhibit contained in PE 0303133F.




