 Justification:
 The FY2027 request for Aircraft Procurement includes 335,973 thousand of discretionary and 162,000 thousand of mandatory (reconciliation) for a total of 497,973 thousand. The discretionary funds provide for
 Correction of Deficiency, Block 4, APG-85 Radar, Propulsion, and Reliability & Maintainability modification and retrofit products. The mandatory funds provide for Block 4 modification and retrofit products.

 Install costs for ECP kits procured with mandatory (reconciliation) funding will still remain as baseline requirements in FY28-To Complete.

 Basis for FY 2027 budget request is to continue to fund the F-35A Total Active Inventory of 541 aircraft. FY 2027 funding increased as a result of an increase in number of Modification Kits being procured in FY
 2027.




